# Leave blank in dev — Vite proxy forwards /api to localhost:4000.
#
# Production:
#   If the SPA and API share the same domain (recommended — nginx reverse
#   proxies /api to Node), leave this BLANK so requests are same-origin.
#   That dodges CORS entirely.
#
#   If you serve the SPA from a different origin (e.g. CDN) and the API
#   from fms.onmobilise.com, set the absolute origin here BEFORE running
#   `npm run build`:
#       VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://fms.onmobilise.com
#   …and add that same origin to CORS_ORIGIN in the backend .env.
VITE_API_BASE_URL=
